OL,3,CNI hospitality sector: Rate
OL,4,Crevaluation is the 'final nail in the
OL,5,Ccoffin'
OL,7,FThe hospitality sector say rates
OL,8,Fincreases after a revaluation of
OL,9,Fbusiness properties here will be the
OL,10,Ffinal nail in the industry's coffin.
OL,12,FOne company owner, Ronan Sweeney, said
OL,13,Fhe is going to see an #85,000 rates
OL,14,Fbill increase next year.
OL,16,FLand and property services say the
OL,17,Flast valuation took place during Covid
OL,18,Fand any discounts during that period
OL,19,Fhave been removed.
