OL,5,Ccoffin'
OL,7,FHowever the majority of Northern
OL,8,FIreland businesses are expected to see
OL,9,F"little or no change" in rates as a
OL,10,Fdraft list of revaluations for
OL,11,Fcommercial properties has been
OL,12,Freleased.
OL,14,FThe Department of Finance has
OL,15,Findicated that properties that have
OL,16,Fseen above average increases in their
OL,17,Fvalue will likely see their overall
OL,18,Frating liability increase, resulting
OL,19,Fin a higher rate bill.
