OL,4,Crevaluation is the 'final nail in the
OL,5,Ccoffin'
OL,7,FSpeaking on the rates hike, Ronan
OL,8,FSweeney, who owns a number of
OL,9,Frestaurants and is investing in Cyrpus
OL,10,FAvenue in Belfast now expects a
OL,11,Fsignificant increase to his overall
OL,12,Frates bill across his properties.
OL,14,FSpeaking on the rates hike he said:
OL,15,F"Having logged onto the website for
OL,16,FLand & Property Services, we were
OL,17,Ftotally flabbergasted to find out our
OL,18,Frates bill is going to increase by
OL,19,Fabout #85,000 next year, and that's
OL,20,Ffor three country pubs that we operate.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
