OL,3,CNI hospitality sector: Rate
OL,4,Crevaluation is the 'final nail in the
OL,5,Ccoffin'
OL,7,F"The simplest thing and most
OL,8,Fstraightforward would be to add 15% to
OL,9,Four company turnover, but as anybody
OL,10,Fin the industry knows at the minute,
OL,11,Fthat's an impossible ask.
OL,13,F"To try and garner that from your
OL,14,Fexisting customers is going to mean
OL,15,Fincredible price rises. There will be
OL,16,Fclosures in hospitality; it's just a
OL,17,Fmatter of how many and when."
