OL,4,Crevaluation is the 'final nail in the
OL,5,Ccoffin'
OL,7,FLand & Property Services (LPS) is
OL,8,Fencouraging businesses to view the
OL,9,Fdraft list which will be used to
OL,10,Fcalculate business rates from April 1
OL,11,F2026.
OL,13,FThe 2026 project has revalued more
OL,14,Fthan 75,000 properties, with an
OL,15,Fapproximate 15% increase in the total
OL,16,Fvalue of non-domestic properties
OL,17,Facross Northern Ireland since the last
OL,18,Frevaluation was carried out in October
OL,19,F2021.
