OL,4,Crevaluation is the 'final nail in the
OL,5,Ccoffin'
OL,7,FNon-domestic rates generate around
OL,8,F#720 million a year, and the
OL,9,FDepartment of Finance says
OL,10,Frevaluations do not raise additional
OL,11,Fincome but are adjusted to maintain
OL,12,Frevenue neutrality.
OL,14,FCommissioner of Valuation for Northern
OL,15,FIreland Angela McGrath said the 2026
OL,16,Frevaluation was "about ensuring that
OL,17,Frates are distributed fairly based on
OL,18,Fcurrent rental evidence".
