OL,7,F"LPS will review any new or relevant
OL,8,Finformation ratepayers wish to bring
OL,9,Fforward now and make updates where
OL,10,Fappropriate before the new valuation
OL,11,Flist takes effect in April 2026."
OL,13,FThe revaluation project shows overall
OL,14,Fgrowth in the valuation list of 15%
OL,15,Facross all property sectors.
