OL,3,CNI hospitality sector: Rate
OL,4,Crevaluation is the 'final nail in the
OL,5,Ccoffin'
OL,7,FWhile some hospitality businesses will
OL,8,Fsee a decrease in their valuation this
OL,9,Ftime round, the majority will see a
OL,10,Fsubstantial increase due to factors
OL,11,Fsuch as improved conditions post-
OL,12,Fpandemic, and expansion and
OL,13,Fimprovement work to premises.
OL,15,FThe Department of Finance said that
OL,16,Falthough the revaluation was revenue
OL,17,Fneutral overall, individual rate
OL,18,Fliabilities would shift, meaning that
OL,19,Fa percentage increase in a property's
OL,20,Fvalue would not lead to a rate bill
OL,21,Frising by the same percentage.
